Hippo_Ajax_Form Class
=====================

Table of Contents:
  0. Requirements
  1. Deploy Files
  2. Yes! Run the Demo
  
0. Requirements: 
------------------------------------------------------------
<> PHP 4.0.3 or higher (4.3.3 recommended)
<> ICONV module installed, for unicode chars conversion.
   (plz review the installation guide from http://tw.php.net/manual/tw/ref.iconv.php)
   
   *if you don't wanna install ICONV module now, you may download Tatter Tools function
    just put 'iconv.php' in the root and follow the script:
   
   if (!function_exists("iconv")) { include("iconv.php");}
   

1. Deploy Files
------------------------------------------------------------
<> create a directory of your web root, then put all .php files in the same directory, ex:

/Hippo_Ajax_Form/
  +-hippo_ajax_form.js
  +-hippo_ajax_form.php
  +-hippo_ajax_form_exec.php
  +-hippo_ajax_form_func.php
  +-index.php
  +-loading.gif

<> those files are:
   /hippo_ajax_form.js                     (JavaScript XML HTTP Request functions)
   /hippo_ajax_form.php                    (Main Hippo_Ajax_Form class)
   /hippo_ajax_form_exec.php               (Main PHP execution file, where you parse form datas)
   /hippo_ajax_form_func.php               (Global Functions)
   /index.php                              (Demo!)
   /loading.gif                            (Execution loading image)
   /COPYING                                (COPYRIGHTS)
   /INSTALL                                (Installation Guide)
   /README                                 (What? u're reading this file, remember?)


2. Yes! Run the Demo
------------------------------------------------------------
http://your.domain.name/Hippo_Ajax_Form/index.php

just put thos files on your site, amd simply run index.php, see ? how easy !!

